Wing . Tegula brownish-yellow, basicosta yellow. Subcostal sclerite yellow, without setulae, only with pale microtomentum. Veins yellow, darkening somewhat distally. No costal spine. Node at base of vein R 2 + 3 and R 4 + 5 bare below (
